Package network

Interface ServerInterface

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.rmi.Remote
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ServerMethods
    public interface ServerInterface
extends java.rmi.Remote
    RMI server interface. Documentation for the methods in this class are specified in ServerMethods which implements them. This excludes the "message..." methods which serve as a bridge between the client and the controller (Game class) and are specified (without the "message prefix") in the controller.
